# CI/CD and Release Engineering

Owners: CI/CD Engineer and Release and Deployment Engineer.

Cover Jenkins, GitHub Actions, GitLab CI/CD, Azure Pipelines, CircleCI, Tekton, Argo CD, Flux, pipeline architecture, quality gates, artifacts, environments, promotions, progressive delivery, rollback, release evidence, and DORA metrics.

Use `.cursor/skills/ci-cd-release-engineering/SKILL.md` and `docs/ci-cd-release-engineering-workflows.md`.

Stop on requested build/test/pipeline/deployment execution, signing or publication, mutable artifact promotion, secret exposure, real endpoints, missing rollback path, unsupported platform assumptions, or missing human approval.
